   News

180,000 bees take centre stage at the Lyon Convention Centre!

   Currently buzzing away in their three colourful hives on the rooftops
   of the Lyon Convention Centre, the venue’s latest tenants arrived in
   their new home at the end of April between the Rhône River and the Tête
   d'Or Park. A truly ideal place in which to live out a happy and
   productive life.

   See all news
   (BUTTON) (BUTTON)
   2

   The Lyon Convention Centre is a GL Events venue and is part of «Lyon
   for Events» It is a unique European prestigious city-centre events
   complex, located in the heart of the Renzo Piano designed Cité
   Internationale and hosts over 3000 events per year. The Lyon Convention
   Center offers 24,000 m² of flexible meeting spaces including 3
   amphitheaters and 35 fully equipped meeting rooms, which can
   accommodate events upto 19,000 people. These spaces are independent and
   dedicated to conventions, seminars, congresses, exhibitions,
   prestigious evening functions, gala dinners and concerts.
   Lyon for Events

